OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out at derelict
OL,4,Chotel in Torquay
OL,6,FA large fire has broken out at a
OL,7,Fderelict hotel in Torquay, for the
OL,8,Fsecond time in three days.
OL,10,FFire and police crews have been in
OL,11,Fattendance at the former 'Sherwood
OL,12,FHotel' on Belgrave Road since 2pm this
OL,13,Fafternoon (Sunday 5th April).
OL,15,FThere was another fire in the building
OL,16,Fon Friday evening, and there have been
OL,17,Fseveral others at the derelict site in
OL,18,Frecent years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
