OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1775555970
OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out at derelict
OL,4,Chotel in Torquay
OL,6,FFollowing today's fire, local
OL,7,Fresidents have been asked to keep
OL,8,Ftheir windows and doors shut because
OL,9,Fof the large amount of smoke.
OL,11,FBelgrave Road has been closed both
OL,12,Fways with slow moving traffic from
OL,13,FFalkland Road to the A379, Torbay
OL,14,FRoad. Emergency services are asking
OL,15,Fpeople to avoid the area.
OL,17,FPolice are asking any witnesses or
OL,18,Fthose with CCTV footage, Ring Doorbell
OL,19,Ffootage etc, to get in touch on 101,
OL,20,Fquoting log number 348 of 05/04/2026.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
